####  6.2.2. <a name='Samplemanifestinstructions'></a>Sample manifest instructions

Instructions for Mac users

1. Run the `md5` command on the .csv file and direct the output to the .manifest file
   
   `md5 Telco123_1579132799000_Migration.csv > Telco123_1579132799000_Migration.manifest` 

3. Hand-edit into proper JSON format 
   
   `Telco123_1579132799000_Migration.manifest` 

4. Run the `zip -r` command to compress the .csv and .manifest files into a .zip file
   
   `zip -r Telco123_1579132799000_Migration.zip Telco123_1579132799000_Migration.manifest.csv Telco123_1579132799000_Migration.manifest` 
 
For the Linux operating system use `MD5sum` and for Windows use `md5`.

